{
 "name": "RPlog_Nar_Shaddaa_-_Sabrina_s_Rescue_1",
 "title": "Nar Shaddaa - Sabrina's Rescue (Part 1)",
 "summary": "Aboard the freighter Voidstalker, the pilot Rook, her astromech Spanner, and Luke Skywalker make the tedious run to Nar Shaddaa on a mission to rescue Sabrina from Galla the Hutt's cargo facility. Luke meditates and resolves that the mission is less about saving a lover than preserving life, while Rook and the droids prepare the ship's disguise as the 'Sideslip' and plan a low-key approach. R2-D2 masks the transponder and scans Galla's facility as they slip past weapon emplacements and talk their way down to a landing pad. With the ship down and dark, Luke takes a comlink and heads aft to join Ai'kani and Snarl, leaving Rook to guard their means of escape.",
